This map was created originally by Cleav420

This is #13 map i have made.

Removed most player-clips.
There was too many player-clips in this map in the first place.
As well i added a few more props/ladders and roofs.
And for the campers in the small spawn storage rooms.
The doors are now brakeable :)

Now this map is not big so there will be a zm_storage_rentals_final
soon and thats it on this map.
On final i will add a 3d skybox as well too.

If theres anything im missing or needed to end this map let me know.

Enjoy the map and please leave comment about map.

Also if any one likes the few maps i made you can x-fire me @ cleav420
Or visit my ventrilo for info on how to better my maps,

Or even work with me together on one of my maps.
Thx .:{Cleav420}:.
